tolong Jay-jay, bukan saya?

479
00:22:52,242 --> 00:22:55,704
<i>[Seksyen E budak lelaki mengusik]</i>

480
00:22:55,912 --> 00:22:56,912
Awak sangat kecut.

481
00:22:57,539 --> 00:22:58,582
