618
00:29:01,861 --> 00:29:02,861
Makan tengah hari.

619
00:29:03,112 --> 00:29:05,990
Oh ya!
Mereka berdua sedang menunggu kita.

620
00:29:06,042 --> 00:29:07,042
<i>Jom.</i> Akhirnya, Jay, awak di sini.
Kami telah berada di sini selama-lamanya.

621
00:29:09,494 --> 00:29:12,621
