633
00:29:30,139 --> 00:29:31,515
Menggoda.

634
00:29:31,516 --> 00:29:32,516
Biarlah mereka. Mereka memberi saya rama-rama. mereka
hanya kembali bersama baru-baru ini.

635
00:29:32,850 --> 00:29:36,479
Oh. Ini makanan awak.

636
00:29:37,105 --> 00:29:38,773
Sejuk!

637
00:29:40,316 --> 00:29:41,651
Kami sangat kebuluran!

638
00:29:41,985 --> 00:29:43,318
Terima kasih, Jay.

639
00:29:43,319 --> 00:29:44,445
Kami sudah lama di sini.

640
